  "text": "• Figure 3 shows a wire-frame drawing of the model for a 3-point plug, the edges extracted from the first frame of Sequence 1 using the Canny operator [CITATION_1] (thresholded on edge-strength), the segmentation of the first frame, and the edgelet flow chart between the first and second frames (produced using Barnard & Thomsons algorithm).",
